{"tid":781669,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【犯罪家族】黃桂芬留下遺書:「對唔住家人」","createTime":"2018-08-16T05:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T06:15:22.000Z","uid":65346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6e463a95f5b75a521f102500d870114f5127a785","tid":781669,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180816/58569895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180816%2F58569895&d=gTfLgwJWevtDncjWVkyqDuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=f16b64ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180816%2F58569895&h=d0f84741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180816/58569895</a><br />\n<br />\n在油麻地停車場墮樓斃命的黃桂芬，經警方調查後，相信他是墮樓自殺。消息透露，黃桂芬昨傍晚獲保釋候查後，乘的士返回九龍塘大宅，與家人晚飯後，他向家人表示想出外行逛一陣，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其朋友</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遂駕駛私家車接載他，他表示要到油麻地，其友人將車泊在油麻地停車場後，黃桂芬著友人幫他到便利店買東西，疑支開友人後，獨自留在停車場。<br />\n<br />\n黃的友人買東西後，折返停車場途中，突聽到一聲巨響，趕返現場已驚見黃桂芬倒在地上，立即報警求助。警員在其身上撿獲他的身份證，確認是黃桂芬，惟他傷重送院後不治。<br />\n警方稍後在私家車的車廂內找到黃的財物，並留下一封寫給家人的遺書，而停車場的cctv亦脗合黃友人的證供，黃留下遺書透露，「對唔住家人，感到將來冇希望，好難行」，顯示尋死之念。警方經調查後，相信黃桂芬支開友人後，在8樓停車場攀過欄河一躍而下，事件並無可疑。"},{"pid":"bf72acf34592acdc40cc5eeb8091ff145b1eef7c","tid":781669,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"找數"},{"pid":"e94d60400235ccc5a4fa65c9bb77d33be61c6b9e","tid":781669,"uid":146066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T05:46:36.000Z